text: Ona Juknevičienė (born April 28, 1955 in Trakai) is a Lithuanian politician and former Member of the European Parliament, part of the European Democrat Party and Alliance of Liberals and Democrats for Europe. ==References== * Ona JUKNEVIČIENĖ. European Parliament.
